title: Martellus Bennett shares adorable picture of daughter
text:
Following a 22-20 win over Oakland Sunday, Bears tight end Martellus Bennett posted quite possibly the most adorable photo of his daughter, Jett.
A photo posted by Martellus Bennett (@martellusb) on Oct 4, 2015 at 3:54pm PDT
Baby girl looks ready to play, though daddy didn’t need much help out there today. With 11 receptions for 83 yards and a touchdown, Bennett was Chicago’s leading receiver in both yards and receptions.
Martellus Bennett 5 yard TD reception to make it 14-13 Raiders pic.twitter.com/XvH1RFI8oN
— THE MAIN MANN™ (@JacobMann_1) October 4, 2015
The real question: Did Jett inherit those mad dance moves too?
